      "audio_segments": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "深夜，汪淼站在窗前，望着天空中闪烁的星星。最近几天，他总是被一些奇怪的现象困扰着。每当他闭上眼睛，就会看到一串神秘的数字在眼前跳动。",
          "audio_path": "tests/backend/stage5/mockdata/audio/scene_001_narration.mp3",
          "duration": 14.496,
          "start_time": 0.0,
          "voice": "BV001_streaming"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这到底是什么？",
          "audio_path": "tests/backend/stage5/mockdata/audio/scene_001_dialogue_001.mp3",
          "duration": 1.128,
          "start_time": 14.496,
          "voice": "BV002_streaming",
          "character": "char_001",
          "character_name": "Wang Miao",
          "emotion": "Anxious and confused"
        }
      ],
      "total_duration": 15.624
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_002",
      "audio_segments": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "第二天，汪淼来到实验室，决定用科学的方法来解开这个谜团。他打开了显微镜，但令他震惊的是，在镜头里，那串数字再次出现了。就在这时，他的助手小李走了进来。",
          "audio_path": "tests/backend/stage5/mockdata/audio/scene_002_narration.mp3",
          "duration": 15.96,
          "start_time": 0.0,
          "voice": "BV001_streaming"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "不可能！",
          "audio_path": "tests/backend/stage5/mockdata/audio/scene_002_dialogue_001.mp3",
          "duration": 1.032,
          "start_time": 15.96,
          "voice": "BV002_streaming",
          "character": "char_001",
          "character_name": "Wang Miao",
          "emotion": "Shocked and distressed"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "汪教授，您今天看起来不太好。",
          "audio_path": "tests/backend/stage5/mockdata/audio/scene_002_dialogue_002.mp3",
          "duration": 2.616,
          "start_time": 16.992,
          "voice": "BV123_streaming",
          "character": "char_002",
          "character_name": "Xiao Li",
          "emotion": "Concerned and caring"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我遇到了一些奇怪的事情。",
          "audio_path": "tests/backend/stage5/mockdata/audio/scene_002_dialogue_003.mp3",
          "duration": 1.848,
          "start_time": 19.608,
          "voice": "BV002_streaming",
          "character": "char_001",
          "character_name": "Wang Miao",
          "emotion": "Anxious and seeking help"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "汪教授，我建议您去见一个人。她叫叶文洁，是红岸基地的前工程师。",
          "audio_path": "tests/backend/stage5/mockdata/audio/scene_002_dialogue_004.mp3",
          "duration": 6.144,
          "start_time": 21.456,
          "voice": "BV123_streaming",
          "character": "char_002",
          "character_name": "Xiao Li",
          "emotion": "Serious and advisory"
        }
      ],
      "total_duration": 27.6
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_003",
      "audio_segments": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "几天后，汪淼驱车来到了郊外的一座老房子前。门开了，一位满头银发但目光深邃的老人站在门口。房间里，叶文洁给汪淼倒了一杯茶，然后缓缓开口。",
          "audio_path": "tests/backend/stage5/mockdata/audio/scene_003_narration.mp3",
          "duration": 15.192,
          "start_time": 0.0,
          "voice": "BV001_streaming"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "叶文洁教授，我是汪淼。",
          "audio_path": "tests/backend/stage5/mockdata/audio/scene_003_dialogue_001.mp3",
          "duration": 2.208,
          "start_time": 15.192,
          "voice": "BV002_streaming",
          "character": "char_001",
          "character_name": "Wang Miao",
          "emotion": "Nervous and respectful"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我知道你会来。进来吧，有些事情，是时候让你知道了。",
          "audio_path": "tests/backend/stage5/mockdata/audio/scene_003_dialogue_002.mp3",
          "duration": 5.808,
          "start_time": 17.4,
          "voice": "BV157_streaming",
          "character": "char_003",
          "character_name": "Ye Wenjie",
          "emotion": "Calm and knowing"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这个宇宙，远比你想象的要复杂。",
          "audio_path": "tests/backend/stage5/mockdata/audio/scene_003_dialogue_003.mp3",
          "duration": 3.408,
          "start_time": 23.208,
          "voice": "BV157_streaming",
          "character": "char_003",
          "character_name": "Ye Wenjie",
          "emotion": "Wise and profound"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "所以，那串数字是...",
          "audio_path": "tests/backend/stage5/mockdata/audio/scene_003_dialogue_004.mp3",
          "duration": 2.088,
          "start_time": 26.616,
          "voice": "BV002_streaming",
          "character": "char_001",
          "character_name": "Wang Miao",
          "emotion": "Trembling with fear"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "是倒计时。三体文明正在接近地球。",
          "audio_path": "tests/backend/stage5/mockdata/audio/scene_003_dialogue_005.mp3",
